So Pat is a successful man
of stage and screen.

52:30.059 --> 52:32.235
For example, he
has a recurring role

52:32.236 --> 52:34.106
in an early 2000' crime drama

52:34.107 --> 52:37.196
and with that money,
he buys an apartment.

52:37.197 --> 52:39.459
And he's living
high on the hog.

52:39.460 --> 52:41.766
People love him
and he's got a wife,

52:41.767 --> 52:44.116
and soon he'll have a son.

52:44.117 --> 52:46.771
And everybody is living
high on the hog

52:46.772 --> 52:51.645
