and he can't book.

52:51.646 --> 52:54.648
And the residuals
only take him so far.

52:54.649 --> 52:56.955
And his wife is a poet,

52:56.956 --> 52:58.522
which to her credit,

52:58.523 --> 53:02.221
she did start teaching
adult ESL classes at night.

53:02.222 --> 53:05.485
But it's not gonna put the boy
through college.

53:05.486 --> 53:07.923
So Patty boy starts to panic.

53:09.882 --> 53:11.578
And another
actor friend of his

53:11.579 --> 53:13.232
sells blenders on commission.

53:13.233 --> 53:17.628
So on his darkest day,
Pat signs on.

53:17.629 --> 53:19.804
And you know what?
He's amazing.

53:19.805 --> 53:23.547
He's great at selling
toasters and blenders.

53:23.548 --> 53:26.202
He's so good, in
